title: Ep 30: Groupie Tales feat Rotimi

description:
You'll have to excuse us if we interrupted a bit, we were both way too fired up having Rotimi in the studio!! Rotimi actor/musician, known as Dre on the hit show Power, just released Jeep Music Vol 1. Rotimi comes in the studio with us for an interview to tell all about African polygamy, his kinks, lets Weezy try to convince him to join her at a sex party, golden showers, and his take on f**king his fans!
